STEPS TO MAKE VHX BUILD

Compile VHX binary
Copy VHX binary into staging
Run create standalone script

Fix permissions with script
Set CloudsData/run and CloudsData/vhx to writeable by all
Create a Working twitter folder

Open project file
Build the package
Replace the icon on the package
Open the default CLOUDS.dmg in Disk Image
Replace the package
Unmount the CLOUDS disk image
Right click and select “Convert CLOUDS.dmg” 
Save as CLOUDS_1_x_x.dmg
This is the new build!